<li><small><a href="http://nobsword.blogspot.com/1993_10_17_nobsword_archive.html" class="external text" title="http://nobsword.blogspot.com/1993_10_17_nobsword_archive.html" rel="nofollow"><i>A Study of History</i></a></small>
