<li><small>With <a href="/wiki/Philip_Toynbee" title="Philip Toynbee">Philip Toynbee</a>, <i>Comparing Notes: A Dialogue across a Generation</i> (Weidenfeld &amp; Nicolson 1963). "Conversations between Arnold Toynbee and his son, Philip … as they were recorded on tape."</small></li>
